hooks.prompt:
Analyze the conversation and check if any Kotlin files (src/main/kotlin/**/*.kt or src/test/kotlin/**/*.kt) were created or modified.

If YES (Kotlin files were changed):
1. Check if './gradlew build' was executed AND succeeded after the changes
2. If build was NOT run or FAILED:
   - Respond with ONLY: {"ok": false, "message": "Build verification needed"}
3. If build SUCCEEDED, check if implementation files (src/main/kotlin) were changed:
   - If yes: Respond with ONLY: {"ok": false, "message": "REQUIREMENTS.md review needed"}
   - If only test files changed: Respond with ONLY: {"ok": true}

If NO (no Kotlin files changed):
- Respond with ONLY: {"ok": true}

IMPORTANT: Respond with ONLY the JSON object, no other text.
